First create a user using unix command: adduser {username}
switch to the user using unix command: su - {username}
execute psql
list all databases using: \l
use a database : \c {databasename}
list all tables using : \d
use  a table : \d {tablename}


when first initializing database set spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=create-drop
copy script in openforumschema.sql and execute query in plsql, ie create database
set spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=validate


